            <h2>How to Find Us</h2>

            <p>We are located at <strong>7 Struan Road, Glasgow G44 3AT</strong> in the Cathcart
            area of Glasgow's south side.</p>

            <!-- GOOGLE MAP -->
            <div class="map-container">
