            <!-- COMING BY CAR -->
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-card-header">
                    <h3>Coming by Car</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="section-card-body">
                    <p>There is limited on-street parking around the church on Struan Road and
                    Kildare Road. Please be aware that it can be particularly busy for parking
                    when there are events on at the nearby Couper Institute.</p>
                    <p>We do not have any designated parking for Blue Badge holders.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- COMING BY PUBLIC TRANSPORT -->
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-card-header">
                    <h3>Coming by Public Transport</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="section-card-body">

                    <h4>By Bus</h4>
                    <p>First Bus services 4 and 6 stop nearby on Clarkston Road, a short walk
                    from the church. Please check the First Bus website for current timetables:</p>
                    <p><a href="https://www.firstgroup.com/greater-glasgow" target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener">firstgroup.com/greater-glasgow</a></p>

                    <h4>By Train</h4>
                    <p>Cathcart Railway Station is approximately 400 metres from the church —
                    around a 5-minute walk.</p>
                    <p>The following ScotRail services stop at Cathcart:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The Cathcart Circle Line from Glasgow Central</li>
                        <li>The Neilston Line from Glasgow Central</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Please note that the Newton train does not stop at Cathcart.</p>
                    <p>Check ScotRail timetables at
                    <a href="https://www.scotrail.co.uk/plan-your-journey/timetables-and-routes"
                    target="_blank" rel="noopener">scotrail.co.uk</a></p>

                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ONLINE -->
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-card-header">
                    <h3>Joining Us Online</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="section-card-body">
                    <p>If you are unable to join us in person, our Sunday service is available
                    on Zoom and is livestreamed on our YouTube channel every week.</p>
                    <p>To receive Zoom details please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
                    <p>Watch on YouTube:
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@cathcartufchurch7834/videos"
                    target="_blank" rel="noopener">youtube.com/@cathcartufchurch7834</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

